<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=98304759499097></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f98304759499097><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=9&mid=98304759499097>Alchemy Guide</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=9&mid=98304759499097#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=6567><span id= >Nitsujlak</span></a>, <span id= > </span><br><span id=notbold>163 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sat, Feb 24th 3:46 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.77]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2> First off i wouldnt advise starting alchemy till 30.. the skill cap for alchemy is your level minus 24 times 5. So if oyu are level 30 its <br>30-24=6<br>6x5=30&nbsp;&nbsp;<br>SO... the skill cap at level 30 is 30 skill. What i am doing to level in alchemy is make nothing but SoW potions... do this till you you are trivial in alchemy. First you need a medicine bag from an alchemy merchan. The recipe for Sow potions (Blood of Wolf) Birthwart (2pp) Fenugreek (2pp) Wolf Blood (1pp). Put one of each herb in the bag and hit combine. If you use only training points to level the skill then you should succeed about half the time (i have 154 wis). So the cost to make is about 10pp a potion. I sell SOW potions for 12-15pp. After you are trivial in Sow potions (skill 37) make shrink potions. Recipe for shrink potions AKA Ant's potions is:  Sumbal(4pp) and Celendine Herb (5pp). I sell these potions for 16-20pp to players. Shrink potions are trivial at 70. After this its up to you.. it gets a lil too expensive to proceed further so I would just stop. Doing alchemy this way will actually make you money instead of losing it for you. An optional thing to do is get a bearskin potion bag and put 10 potions inside then hit combine. It will make a 10 charge potion of tat kind. I have found that people will buy your wares much more likely if they are 10 charges. <br><br>Im considering sending this guide to various sites.. so PLEASE rate it.<br><br>Nitsujlak 30 shm (used to have a 40 shm till i shut off my account) <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
