	   <tr><td colspan=2>Eastern Wastes at lvl 30 might be pretty rough, in my opinion (I was there at 36 and spent the whole time thinking I should wait till lvl 40 or so to go back....the blues there are wikkid...I wouldn't recommend EW to a lvl 30 at all).&nbsp;&nbsp;You might, however, go thru EW to the rygorr fort and go to Crystal Caverns to hunt there.  Nice drops and nice xp.  Also, you might consider hunting snow cougars off the Velious docks (with a partner or group).  The xp with them is sweet and the occasional drop of a cougar claw earring is always welcome.  Also for your lvl, there is Frontier Mountains (not so great xp with the giants, but there's the chance of some nice loot).<br><br>Rathe Mtns, I couldn't tell you, except maybe doing cyclops and giant skellies in group.  I never hunted much there until I was high enough lvl to group for the giants there.<br><br>Good luck!<br>&nbsp;<br>Badjur<br>54 Barbarian Shaman (Druzzil Ro)<br><br>Aepox Weeblatter<br>35 Dwarf Warrior</td></tr>
