	   <tr><td colspan=2>Greetings,<br><br>Personally, I use a Slime Coated Harpoon as opposed to a blunt weapon. There are several reasons that I would recommend a piercer over blunt.<br><br>One - Our epic is a piercer. You need a decent skill level for it.<br><br>Two - You job after about 20 or so is not a tank. You don't need a high damage weapon. You outdamage the tank and you will die faster.<br><br>Three - You primary job is a healer/buffer/debuffer. I know you know this. No offense, but the weapons are secondary. Keep the blunt and piercing balanced.<br><br>So, bottom line, I would recommend keeping each of the items in the bank and swap em out. But wait to melee until tanks have jumped in first.<br><br>For 1H blunt, I recommend a Blackjack. At 23, you can pick one up for about 400 or so. For 2H blunt, I recommend either a Gatorsmash Maul or a Drakkel Forged hammer. For a piercer, I would recommend an Ebon War Spear.<br><br>Peace...<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
