	   <tr><td colspan=2>There is a fun quest you can do killing ice goblin scouts, for a magical 1hb.&nbsp;&nbsp;Find Bandl wall.  After some time you will come to two (the guard all by himself).  He stands against one wall and faces the other, follow the opsite igloos.  Kill these scouts, a caster goblin (i forget its name) will spawn and drop some beads that are truned in for the hammer.  Also you can hunt the tundra near Bandl.  There are a number of towers out on the tundra which are normaly safe places to med.  You can hunt the tundra and BB until at least lvl 14.  There are some other nice quest in everfrost.  Everfrost is a great place to grow up so don't leave it too soon.<br><br>Yodan<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
