	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Is there a str bonus diffrence between spears and Two Hand Blunt weapons?<br><br>With a 2hb weapon I get as much as 36 damage points over the expected damage.&nbsp;&nbsp;That is<br>2(damage rate)+ 36.  <br><br>Something to consider while soloing.  A while back I did a comparasion between using a Mortificators Staff and the JCP and CGS combo. Based on Hp lost and mana used there was no major differance between the two.  Yes I had the same weapon skill for both weapon types.  <br><br>Now at lvl 46 I can solo a Frost Giant Berserker with a Runewood Great Staff, but I can not solo one with a Mortiticators Staff.  <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
