	   <tr><td colspan=2>emotes are very cool. I have many set up for my Shaman. I don't do much pulling so most of emotes are hotkeys for grouping. <br>Examples:<br><br>In Hotkey page 4 slot 1:<br>HEAL<br>&lt;social codes&gt;: <br>line 1: /g &lt;your character name&gt; begins to chant. %T wound passes into &lt;your character name&gt;. The chant stops.<br>line 2: cast 1 <br><br>Follow the same idea for as many hotkeys you want.. for grouping.. for soloing and buffing others use the /say command instead.. etc.. hope you get the picture..have fun with it. Some people will appreciate it other will not.. but you know what I always say about that.. :) KMA<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
