	   <tr><td colspan=2>All good points.&nbsp;&nbsp;Heres a few other pointers<br>1) Skip killing the wolves, it just makes the wolves of the world mad at you and gives little in return.<br><br>2) When traveling the Halas-BB route follow this simple path:  Take the first left(east) from the Halas ramp out to 3 guards (with snowflake). Turn right (south) and scoot along the wall (careful of the gobs at the igloos, you can pass this part later once you get to know the path).  Enter back into the canyons at the next opening and hug the left (south) wall.  Take the first path on your left (careful not to miss it)  this leads to the BB ramp.  Bring a light, its always too dark.  And keep one in the bank for the inevitable CR.<br><br>3) Give white bear pelts to Cindl for some PW armor, or tailor some yourself out of ruined bear pelts.  <br><br>4) Stock up on containers by killing gob whelps and gnoll pups<br><br>5) Around 4-5 try camping an igloo spawn, thier pretty good xp.<br><br>6) Leave everfrost for the world at large far richer than those pesky humans to the south :)<br>&nbsp;<br>Tailen<br>"I'm not a SoW addict, addicts go to meetings. I'm a Shaman!"</td></tr>
